changelog.release_notes:
- fix a vibration interval bug;
- added a custom text when charging the battery;
- added persistent storage for weather text.

data.description:
A simple and customisable watchface that supports:
- 12-H / 24-H time format;
- date display;
- weather information from OpenWeatherMap;
- custom text display;
- battery info;
- hourly vibration;
- Bluetooth disconnect vibration and visual alert;
- many more to come :)
